      "message": "[🟡 Suggestion] Line 194: The message classification prefixes are broad enough to match unrelated future protocol types such as `application/invite-*` or `application/im-gitmessage-identity`, which would bypass the cooldown and force reconnects. Prefer matching the documented exact type plus explicit suffix separators.\n```suggestion\nval isMessage \u003d type \u003d\u003d \"application/im-gitmessage-id\"\n        || type.startsWith(\"application/im-gitmessage-id/\")\n        || type \u003d\u003d \"application/invite\"\n        || type.startsWith(\"application/invite+\")\n```",
